    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you can expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. Externally, the paint has some fading on the hood and roof, along with a few noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear bumper. The interior is intact but shows significant wear on the upholstery and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind doing a bit of cosmetic or minor mechanical upkeep.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
